additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: POISON KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN READ SAFETY DIRECTIONS When Drano Kitchen Crystals are used in accordance with the directions, no lasting damage to plastic pipes, septic tanks or environment will be incurred. Will only work in S bends and will not work through tree roots, leaves and other non-organic matter. Do not plug the drain pipe or use a plunger while Drano Kitchen Crystals is in the drain pipe. Do not use on aluminium. PRECAUTIONS: DO NOT USE IN TOILETS, dishwashers, garbage disposals, spas, washing machines or any pipes leading to those outlets.
